HEADWORD: Pean
<hw>Pean</hw> <pr>(p⟦emac⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>pene</ets>, F. <ets>panne</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>One
